name: indian-contact-call-log-generator
description:
It generate the contact numbers starting from 6,7,8 and 9 for indian number. then it generate call log for that contact for given date range (daily 8-12 with incoming, outgoing and missed call).
You can import directly contact from generated vcf file, for call log you can use SMS Backup & Restore app in playstore
Validate generated data: https://www.synctech.com.au/sms-backup-restore/view-backup/
